quote.summary: Jiangsu Horizon Chain Supermarket Co Ltd is a China-based company principally engaged in supermarket and convenience store retail operations. The Company is primarily engaged in four businesses. The wholesale operations sell grains and oil, food products and other products to resellers and other retail operators including other operators of supermarkets and convenience stores as well as catering business operators. The retail operations operate supermarkets and convenience stores under brand Hongxinlong, as well as Malls. The rental operations engage in the leasing of some shop floor area or shop premises in Retail Stores and Malls to other retail operators like restaurant, hotels and pharmacies. The supply and sales of meals business is engaged in the production of meals and their distribution to local corporates, schools or government entities. The Company mainly conducts its businesses in the domestic market.
